cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.DB 

The paper introduces a novel architecture for early detection of multiple diseases using a multi-resolution convolutional neural network. The paper also proposes a method for differentiable multivariate kernel regression for imputing the temporal sparse observations. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction)
- cs.DB (Databases)
